---
import PageLayout from '../../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';

export const prerender = true;

const lang = 'en';
const title = 'Educational Programs';
const pageTitle = 'Program 6: Educational Programs';
---

<PageLayout title={title} lang={lang} pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <p>The educational programs of the organization are aimed at improving the knowledge and skills of various population groups.</p>
  <p>Trainings, seminars, and professional development courses are conducted on a wide range of topics, including human rights, civic participation, leadership and project management.</p>
  <p>Educational programs are adapted for various target groups: youth, women, civil servants, NGO representatives.</p>
</PageLayout>
